An admin types in their credentials and logs into the system, the admin AdminController class checks 
if the the credentials entered by the user matches the expected values. 
The AuthAdmin class calls the User.getUserById(id) method, which passes the users email address(id) of the logged in user. 
If the type returned is Admin then access is granted. 

When a product categroy is updated the id, name and an array of products are passed through the constructor to be created and
setters are used to create the them.
